{"tid":945330,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想介丁","createTime":"2018-12-17T19:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T16:20:44.000Z","uid":1749,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56d845b66fc03c6c14fd983803a5c297af9a7e06","tid":945330,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T19:45:26.000Z","msg":"自從打響起義第一槍後就不能自拔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以家一得閒就會拎出黎保養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人親身講下手X 過度會發生咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5691146bf3df68e4fe582a7376f7da463ce35e","tid":945330,"uid":198900,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T19:52:10.000Z","msg":"用刀介<br />\n介過度會痛"},{"pid":"9801ddc1f665c34e4a7c9a5d998cbb6caf9402f9","tid":945330,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T20:59:12.000Z","msg":"中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，精既作用係同黎滋潤五臟六腑，同埋可以轉化為腦髓＋骨髓＋血。<br />\n精一失，五臟六腑都會變差，長期落去就會出現好多症狀，導致你變成一個溝唔到女既毒撚。<br />\n<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，出現既症狀都唔同，以下為最常見既症狀：<br />\n<br />\n變樣衰，變猥瑣，臉色灰暗，雙眼無神，脫髮，髮質變差<br />\n暗瘡，臉多油，自卑冇自信，社交恐懼症，耳嗚<br />\n前列線炎，陽痿，早洩，蕁麻疹<br />\n腦力＋思考力＋理解力下解，記性變差<br />\n口臭，體臭，易骨折，聽力下降，講野細聲冇中氣<br />\n易累，體力下降，易怒，腰痛，尿頻<br />\n<br />\n戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw&d=zUnTnZQF7SzdTJuSjdHB2dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1e33b0c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2UMNP_SsDYEJnFfFVw</a><br />\n《戒為良藥》想成功戒一年就睇哂佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=zUnTnZQF7SzdTJuSjdHB2dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d5c83396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"d9b1f9ff0b70466e1d9fabce6bb6dd212f03cd2a","tid":94533